speech.p: On a point of clarity, may I make it clear that the Government do not support clause 108? I apologise for not making that clear before. On making tax digital, I refer colleagues to my statement at the beginning of our debate on the first group of amendments.
Clause 127 ordered to stand part of the Bill.
That clause 127 be transferred to the end of clause 69.(Jane Ellison.)
Clauses 128 to 133 ordered to stand part of the Bill.
